      <context>
         <p>The<uicontrol>Comment Log Report</uicontrol>provides details on all the comments and their responses from the comment log for the selected document. The report displays details chronologically with the latest comment post displayed first.</p>
      </context>
      <ol>
         <li href="../../../Warehouse/Task_Warehouse/AcsPrjContDocsNav.dita#task-5739/AccProContDocFolder">
            <p/>
