            <p>Select the appropriate document, click<uicontrol>Report</uicontrol>, and thenclick<uicontrol>Comment Log Report</uicontrol>.</p>
            <p>The report is generated and displayed.<p>For information on the various features available, refer to <xref href="../../Common_Application_Features/Standard_Report_Functions/StdRepFncts.xml">Standard Report Functions</xref>.</p>
